{"tid":1188931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥同梁振英有咩分別？","createTime":"2019-06-06T14:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:21:07.000Z","uid":249971,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1469c937570bc07ec7a73943e2d27e1aaee60d2a","tid":1188931,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得無分別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTd1Cja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTd1Cja.jpg&h=711e24ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tcttgkH74N0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtcttgkH74N0&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=53979a10\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tcttgkH74N0</a><br />\n佢今年64連提都唔提<br />\n<br />\n你班fans話人紅衛兵？話人逼佢表態？叫佢表態就係想令佢唸起一起直播嘅初衷<br />\n事實係佢真係變咗<br />\n<br />\n某程度上撐達哥同撐梁振英無分別<br />\n撐689=3/5毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsuzXkD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhsuzXkD.gif&h=fd905d84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"591c1f9c1847245e6313535267ee7b1c92214c51","tid":1188931,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b32e10ac8a173d100c2b0ad0b409d3408b4d79","tid":1188931,"uid":197563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"达衛軍全面進場示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38c7346e7c12d316475affbf6b91ac394c8ca89","tid":1188931,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"今日講嘅伎倆，個淵源歷史悠久，任何古文明都用過：分而治之，Divide et impera，將敵人搞到內亂，漁人得利。<br />\n<br />\n但係香港承受緊嘅，係一個共產主義特有嘅version：文化馬克思主義，Cultural Marxism，係馬克思主義傳承落廿一世紀嘅最大產物。大家諗吓近十年有冇係輿論見過以下嘅非黑直白分壘：<br />\n<br />\n港女vs港男 （性別）<br />\n直vs孿（性向）<br />\n廢老vs廢中vs廢青（年齡）<br />\nxx後vs yy後（年齡）<br />\n有錢有樓vs冇錢冇樓（經濟）<br />\n勞工vs文書（工種）<br />\n追韓劇vs追日劇vs追美劇vs追英劇（興趣）<br />\n高學歷vs低學歷（學歷）<br />\n名校vs非名校（學歷）<br />\nHKUvsCUHKvsBUvsUSTvsEdU（學歷）<br />\n已移民vs未移民（國籍）<br />\n黃絲vs藍絲vs綠絲（政治取態）<br />\n好多分完再分嘅政治陣營，互鬥（政治取態）<br />\n<br />\n香港社會，因爲仲未係完全極權統治，所以仲有思想多元嘅空間，可以容納唔同嘅意見。文化馬克思嘅手段，就係將社會中嘅各種多元簡單化，變爲非黑直白，產生感性嘅內鬥，耗損整個社會嘅政治力量。<br />\n<br />\n［重貼］中共思想操縱系列<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1187750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1187750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6faa2cc577d9b19c85d46d83ecd1dcfafc07266","tid":1188931,"uid":37375,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖 上一頁"}]}